flowchart TD
    User["User: /arckit.sobc"] --> SessionHook["hooks/arckit-session.sh<br/>Inject ARCKIT_VERSION"]
    SessionHook --> ContextHook["hooks/arckit-context.sh<br/>Scan projects/artifacts"]
    ContextHook --> Command["commands/sobc.md"]
    
    Command --> CheckProjects["Check projects via hook context"]
    CheckProjects --> SelectProject["Interactive project selection<br/>or PROJECT_ID argument"]
    
    SelectProject --> CheckDeps["Check dependencies:<br/>stakeholders (M)<br/>risk (M)"]
    CheckDeps --> DepsFound{Dependencies<br/>exist?}
    
    DepsFound -->|No| Error["Error: Missing STKE/RISK"]
    DepsFound -->|Yes| ReadDeps["Read ARC-{PID}-STKE-*.md<br/>Read ARC-{PID}-RISK-*.md"]
    
    ReadDeps --> CheckExternal["Check external docs:<br/>projects/{PID}/external/<br/>projects/000-global/policies/"]
    CheckExternal --> ExternalFound{External<br/>docs?}
    
    ExternalFound -->|Yes| ReadExternal["Read external SOW/RFP/<br/>policy/strategy docs"]
    ExternalFound -->|No| SkipExternal["Continue without"]
    
    ReadExternal --> ResolveTemplate
    SkipExternal --> ResolveTemplate
    
    ResolveTemplate["Template resolution:<br/>1. .arckit/templates-custom/sobc-template.md<br/>2. .arckit/templates/sobc-template.md"]
    ResolveTemplate --> Generate["Populate template:<br/>- Strategic Case (goals)<br/>- Economic Case (options)<br/>- Commercial Case (procurement)<br/>- Financial Case (costs)<br/>- Management Case (risks)"]
    
    Generate --> DocID["Generate Document ID:<br/>ARC-{PID}-SOBC-v{VERSION}"]
    DocID --> Metadata["Populate Document Control:<br/>- Status: DRAFT<br/>- Author, Date<br/>- Revision History"]
    
    Metadata --> ValidateHook["hooks/validate-arc-filename.sh<br/>Auto-correct filename"]
    ValidateHook --> SecretHook["hooks/secret-file-scanner.py<br/>Scan for secrets"]
    
    SecretHook --> Write["Write: projects/{PID}/ARC-{PID}-SOBC-v{VERSION}.md"]
    Write --> Output["Generated SOBC document"]
